title: Inside Amazon's new Chicago store which only sells books that got at least 4.5 stars online
text:
March 22, 2017 at 09:27 AM EDT Inside Amazon's new Chicago store which only sells books that got at least 4.5 stars online 
Amazon has just recently opened its fifth bookstore in Chicago that only carries books rated over 4.5 stars online. Take a look inside.
